snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Aas Paas Episode 19 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 20th March 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,
crosses paths with her.
Bound by their selflessness, they embark on a journey where their devotion to family is tested, and their own happiness is put on the line.
Will Arshia succeed in bringing her family back together? What challenges await Dr. Saham and Arshia? Could love blossom between them?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Muhammad Iftikhar Iffi

snippet.title: WATERMELON JELLY | Fresh Colorful Fruit Jelly Recipe Making in Village | Agar Agar Jelly Cooking
snippet.description: This video showcases the making of a healthy, fresh, and natural fruit jelly using a variety of colorful fruits, sugar, and agar agar. The combination of fresh fruits adds natural sweetness and a delightful texture, while agar agar helps create a perfect jelly consistency. This refreshing dessert is not only visually stunning but also a light and healthy treat, made using simple ingredients without any artificial additives. Watch the entire process as we prepare, set, and slice this beautiful jelly, bringing out the flavors of nature’s best ingredients in a traditional village-style preparation.

snippet.title: NZ Vs PAK 2nd T20I | Cricket Highlights | Pakistan Tour Of New Zealand | 18th March 2025
snippet.description:
In the 2nd T20I, New Zealand won the toss and decided to bowl first and invited Pakistan to bat first at the University Oval. Pakistan scored 135 runs for the loss of 9 wickets in their 15 overs. New Zealand chased down the target in just 13.1 overs and won the match by 5 wickets.

snippet.title: 2111: ശരീരത്തിലെ ഏറ്റവും പ്രധാനപ്പെട്ട മസിൽ? Most important muscle in the body
snippet.description:
2111: ശരീരത്തിലെ ഏറ്റവും പ്രധാനപ്പെട്ട മസിൽ? Most important muscle in the body 

ശരീരത്തിൽ പല തരത്തിലുള്ള മസിലുകൾ ഉണ്ട്. ശരീരത്തിലെ ഏറ്റവും പ്രധാനപ്പെട്ട മസിൽ ഏതാണ്? ദൈനംദിന ജീവിതത്തിൽ ഏറ്റവും കൂടുതൽ ഉപയോഗിക്കുന്ന ഈ skeletal  മസിൽ ശക്തമായിരിക്കണം, ഇല്ലെങ്കിൽ പല തരത്തിലുള്ള ബുദ്ധിമുട്ടുകൾ നമുക്ക് വരാം. ശരിയായ പരിശീലനം വഴി ഇവയുടെ ശക്തിയും സ്ഥിരതയും കൂട്ടാൻ കഴിയും. ഈ മസിലുകൾ ശരീരത്തിന് literally support system ആണെന്നു പറയാം!

ഈ വീഡിയോയിൽ എന്താണ് ഉൾപ്പെടുന്നത്:
 • ശരീരത്തിലെ ഏറ്റവും പ്രധാനപ്പെട്ട മസിൽ ഏതാണ്?
 • അതിന്റെ പ്രവർത്തനം എങ്ങനെ?
 • നമ്മുടെ ദിനചര്യയിലും ആരോഗ്യത്തിലും അതിന്റെ പങ്ക്.
 • ഈ മസിൽ ആരോഗ്യകരമായി നിലനിർത്താൻ മാർഗങ്ങൾ.

#drdanishsalim #HeartMuscle #ImportantMuscle #MalayalamHealthTips #HealthEducation #CardiacMuscle #MalayalamYouTube #BodyFacts #HeartCare #HealthyLiving #HealthMalayalam #drdanishsalim #ddbl #ഏറ്റവും_പ്രധാനപെട്ട_മസിൽ

Follow the Dr Danish Salim’s Dr D Better Life channel on WhatsApp: https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029Va94tTk0bIdsmbBBaC0P

*****Dr. Danish Salim*****

Dr Danish Salim; currently working as Specialist Emergency Department, Sheikh Khalifa Medical City, Abu Dubai, UAE Health Authority & Managing Director at Dr D Better Life Pvt Ltd. He was the academic director and head of the emergency department at PRS Hospital, Kerala. He has over 10 years of experience in emergency and critical care. He was awarded the SEHA Hero award and is one of the first doctors to receive a Golden Visa from the UAE Government for his contributions to Health Care.

He was active in the field of emergency medicine and have
contributed in bringing in multiple innovations for which Dr
Danish was awarded nationally as "Best innovator in emergency medicine and young achiever" as well as the “Best emergency physician of state award".

Among multiple innovations like app for accident alerts, jump kits for common emergency management, Dr Danish brought into being the state's first bike ambulance with KED and a single state wide-app to control and coordinate private and public ambulances under one platform with the help of Indian Medical Association and Kerala Police. This network was appreciated and is successfully running with the support of the government of Kerala currently.

Besides the technology field, Dr Danish was enthusiastic in conducting more than 2000 structured emergency training classes for common men, residents, doctors and healthcare professionals over the span of 5 years.

Positions Held

1. Kerala state Secretary: Society for Emergency Medicine India

2. National Innovation Head Society for Emergency Medicine India

3. Vice President Indian Medical Association Kovalam

Episode 4350: Verma Ji Ke Ghar Ka Siren
--------------------------------------------------------
The Gokuldham members grow frustrated with the alarm at Verma Ji's house and find a way to turn it off. Later, the Mahila Mandal admits to attempting to enter the house without permission.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,

snippet.title: होटल जैसा सुपर सॉफ्ट और मुलायम नीर डोसा बनाने का सबसे आसान तरीका | Perfect Neer Dosa Recipe
snippet.description:
Neer dosa South Indian cuisine ka ek anokha aur lajawab hissa hai jo patla, soft aur mukhmein ghulne wala hota hai. Yeh dosa bina fermentation ke jaldi ban jata hai, isliye agar aapko turant kuch halka aur swadisht banana ho to neer dosa best option hai. Coconut chutney, sambar ya kisi bhi sabji ke saath iska swaad aur bhi badh jata hai.

Breakfast, lunch ya dinner, kisi bhi waqt neer dosa enjoy kiya ja sakta hai. Agar aapko yeh neer dosa ki recipe pasand aaye to video ko like karein, share karein aur channel subscribe karna na bhoolen.

hi.description:
Neer dosa South Indian cuisine ka ek anokha aur lajawab hissa hai jo patla, soft aur mukhmein ghulne wala hota hai. Yeh dosa bina fermentation ke jaldi ban jata hai, isliye agar aapko turant kuch halka aur swadisht banana ho to neer dosa best option hai. Coconut chutney, sambar ya kisi bhi sabji ke saath iska swaad aur bhi badh jata hai.

Breakfast, lunch ya dinner, kisi bhi waqt neer dosa enjoy kiya ja sakta hai. Agar aapko yeh neer dosa ki recipe pasand aaye to video ko like karein, share karein aur channel subscribe karna na bhoolen.

snippet.title: आदमी है की ढक्कन, कहा भी नहा लेता है, बाप के ही मज़े ले लिए ! Vijay Raaz Comedy |Kauwa Biryani Comedy
snippet.description:
Hilarious Kauwa Biryani Comedy Scene of Vijay Raaz from Movie: Run (2004)

Dive into the rib-tickling world of "Run" (2004) with these iconic comedy scenes featuring the legendary Vijay Raaz! This Bollywood gem, directed by Jeeva and produced by Boney Kapoor and Sridevi, showcases Vijay Raaz at his comedic best. Watch as he brings laughter to every frame with his impeccable timing and hilarious antics. Relive the unforgettable "Kauwa Biryani" scene, where Vijay Raaz's character hilariously mistakes crow meat for chicken, delivering the classic line, "Yeh kaunsi biryani hai?" The film stars Abhishek Bachchan and Bhoomika Chawla in the lead roles, with a memorable soundtrack composed by Vidyasagar. Whether you're looking for a hearty laugh or just want to relive some classic comedy moments, these scenes are sure to leave you in splits!

फिल्म रन (2004) से विजय राज के मजेदार कौआ बिरयानी कॉमेडी सीन

"रन" (2004) की दुनिया में विजय राज के इन मशहूर कॉमेडी सीन्स के साथ प्रवेश करें! इस बॉलीवुड रत्न को जीव द्वारा निर्देशित किया गया है और बोनी कपूर और श्रीदेवी द्वारा निर्मित किया गया है। फिल्म में अभिषेक बच्चन और भूमिका चावला मुख्य भूमिकाओं में हैं, और इसका यादगार साउंडट्रैक विद्यसागर द्वारा रचित है। विजय राज अपनी बेमिसाल टाइमिंग और मजेदार हरकतों के साथ हर फ्रेम में हंसी का तड़का लगाते हैं। अविस्मरणीय "कौवा बिरयानी" सीन को फिर से जीएं, जहां विजय राज का किरदार कौवे के मांस को चिकन समझकर मजाकिया अंदाज में पूछता है, "ये कौनसी बिरयानी है?" चाहे आपको जोरदार हंसी चाहिए या बस कुछ क्लासिक कॉमेडी पलों को फिर से जीना चाहते हैं, ये सीन निश्चित रूप से आपको हंसते-हंसते लोटपोट कर देंगे!

Enjoy and share the laughter!

Movie: Run (2004)
Cast: Vijay Raaz, Abhishek Bachchan, Bhumika Chawla, Mahesh Manjrekar, Mukesh Rishi.
Music: Himesh Reshammiya, Naresh Sharma
Director: Jeeva
Producer: Boney Kapoor, Sridevi, Surinder Kapoor

snippet.description:

snippet.title: NZ Vs PAK 1st T20I | Cricket Highlights | Pakistan Tour Of New Zealand | 16th March 2025
snippet.description:
In the 1st T20I, New Zealand won the toss and decided to bowl first and invited Pakistan to bat first. Pakistan was cheaply dismissed on the score of 91 runs in 18.4 overs. New Zealand chased down the target in just 10.1 overs and won the match by 9 wickets. 
.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

snippet.title: Sunita Williams धरती पर लौटीं, ये है अंतरिक्ष से पृथ्वी पर लौटने का सिलसिलेवार ब्योरा (BBC Hindi)
snippet.description:
अंतरिक्ष यात्री सुनीता विलियम्स और बुच विलमोर अन्य दो अंतरिक्ष यात्रियों के साथ स्पेसएक्स के ड्रैगन कैप्सूल के ज़रिए पृथ्वी पर लौट आए हैं. बीते साल जून में महज़ आठ दिनों के लिए अंतरराष्ट्रीय स्पेस स्टेशन पर गए ये दोनों एस्ट्रोनॉट नौ महीनों बाद लौट पाए हैं. बोइंग का जो स्टारलाइनर यान उन्हें वापस धरती पर लाने वाला था वो ख़राब हो गया था इसलिए उन्हें इतना लंबा इंतज़ार करना पड़ा. उन्हें आख़िरकार एलन मस्क की कंपनी स्पेसएक्स का ड्रैगन कैप्सूल फ्लोरिडा के तट पर सुरक्षित रूप से उतारा.

अंतरिक्ष यात्रियों को स्पेस स्टेशन से धरती पर पहुँचने में 17 घंटों का लंबा वक्त लगा. पढ़िए कैसी थी ये यात्रा और कैप्सूल के स्पलैशडाउन करने के बाद क्या-क्या हुआ?

#space #nasa #sunitawilliams 

* ऐसे ही और वीडियो देखने के लिए चैनल सब्सक्राइब ज़रूर करें-
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCN7B-QD0Qgn2boVH5Q0pOWg?disable_polymer=true

* बीबीसी हिंदी से आप इन सोशल मीडिया चैनल्स पर भी जुड़ सकते हैं-

फ़ेसबुक- https://www.facebook.com/BBCnewsHindi

snippet.title: Sunita Williams Smiles And Waves At The Camera After Her Safe Return To Earth
snippet.description:
NASA astronauts Sunita Williams and Butch Wilmore have successfully returned to Earth after 9 months in in space. The SpaceX capsule 'Freedom' splashed down at 3:28 a.m., concluding a mission extended due to technical issues. The landing, involving complex de-orbiting and seven crucial phases, proceeded as planned. The astronauts will undergo medical examinations upon return.

Sunita Williams and Butch Wilmore have returned to Earth after an unexpected 286-day stay on the International Space Station (ISS). localized.title: Sunita Williams and Butch Wilmore Return After 286 Days in Space | InNews | Drishti IAS
localized.description:
हमारी टीम द्वारा काउसलिंग लेने के लिए यह फॉर्म भरें:  https://drishti.xyz/Noida-Centre-Hindi
या फिर इस नंबर पर संपर्क करें: 8750187501
लोकेशन:  https://drishti.xyz/Drishti-IAS-Noida
*************************************************************************

Sunita Williams and Butch Wilmore have returned to Earth after an unexpected 286-day stay on the International Space Station (ISS). Originally scheduled for a week, their mission extended due to technical issues with Boeing’s Starliner spacecraft. They were finally brought back by a SpaceX Dragon. This incident offers valuable insights into the effects of prolonged space travel on the human body.

snippet.title: Prithviraj Sukumaran Interview With Baradwaj Rangan | L2E Empuraan | Conversation | Part - 1
snippet.description:
In his part-one interview with Baradwaj Rangan, #prithvirajsukumaran discusses his next big-budget picture #l2empuraan, his filmmaking process, and directing the icon #mohanlal. He also discusses how challenging it is to make a sequel.  Why movies with #Mammooty and #Rajinikanth didn't happen?, How he collabrates with the writer #Muraligopy and a lot more!

Mann Mast Malang Episode 13 Teaser - 16th March 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Mann Mast Malang is a love story that traces the journey of two families who, once close and united by their children's engagement, become sworn enemies due to a single incident. As the story unfolds, Kabeer and Riya, former fiancés turned enemies, start to grow closer and eventually fall in love. Their love story faces the challenge of uniting their feuding families, as they strive to make their love successful against all odds.

snippet.title: Haider Ka Janaza | Salim Merchant | Imran Abidi | Jaaved Jaaferi | Salim Sulaiman | 21 Ramzaan Noha
snippet.description:
Haider Ka Janaza is a heartfelt Noha honoring Hazrat Ali (A.S.), capturing the sorrow and reverence of 21 Ramzaan, the day of His martyrdom. This tribute reflects the deep grief of Imam Ali’s final journey, evoking the pain and loss felt by the faithful 🤍

Subscribe to our channel for more music everyday 🔔

To SUBSCRIBE click the link below:
http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=SalimSulaimanMusic

Audio Credits
Music Composed & Produced by: Salim Sulaiman
Singers: Salim Merchant, Imran Abidi
Recital by: Jaaved Jaaferi
Lyrics: Razi Sahab
Additional Lyrics: Imran Abidi
Originally Recited by: Hassan Abbas
Backing Vocals: Manish Sharma, Vaibhav Rajvarsh, Diptanshu Tiwari, Imran Abidi
Mixed & Mastered by: Tejus Srivastava at Blue Productions
Distributed by Global Music Junction, Warner Music India

Shot by Aaquib Siddique (Black Acid Productions)
Video by Vipin Kaushal (One Man Army)
Special Thanks to Tanveer Khan

Lyrics:

Haider Ke Janaze Ko Hasnain Uthate Hain
Hain Kaise Musalmaan Jo Zahra Ko Rulate Hain

Zainab Yehi Kehti Hain Batlaiye Baba
Gurabat Mein Humein Kis Par Ab Chor Ke Jate Hain

Kulsoom Tadapti Hain Lipti Hui Baba Se
Shabbir Janaze Se Samjha Ke Hatate Hain

Sehme Huye Hain Ghazi, Baithe Huye Hujre Mein
Bhai Ko Shahe Wala Behla Ke Bulate Hain

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: The Lavari Show EP 38 | ft. Paresh Ganatra | Meme Legend | The Comedy Factory
snippet.description:
Special Guest - Paresh Ganatra
Paresh Ganatra is an Indian actor and comedian known for his work in television, films, and theater. He began his acting career during his college days by performing in theater. Paresh made his film debut in 1999 with "Mann" and gained prominence for his role as Praveen Thakkar in the TV series "Baa Bahoo Aur Baby" (2005–2010). He is also known for his performances in films like "No Entry" (2005), "Welcome" (2007), and "Rowdy Rathore" (2012).

Apart from movies and daily soaps, Paresh Ganatra is also well-known for his particiaption in the comedy reality TV shows like “Comedy Circus 3 Ka Tadka,” “Comedy Circus Mahasangram,” and “Comedy Circus Ke SuperStars.” He has also played different characters in “Comedy Nights with Kapil” (2013–2016), and “The Kapil Sharma Show” (2016–2017).

Apart from movies and daily soaps, Paresh Ganatra is also well-known for his particiaption in the comedy reality TV shows like “Comedy Circus 3 Ka Tadka,” “Comedy Circus Mahasangram,” and “Comedy Circus Ke SuperStars.” He has also played different characters in “Comedy Nights with Kapil” (2013–2016), and “The Kapil Sharma Show” (2016–2017).

snippet.title: Tigmanshu Dhulia's The Promise – A Must-Watch | Royal Stag Barrel Select Shorts
snippet.description:
In Tigmanshu Dhulia's poignant masterpiece ‘The Promise,’ Royal Stag Barrel Select Shorts delivers a soul-stirring tale that exemplifies the best of select storytelling.

When Delhi newcomer Chitra (played by Priyamani) crosses paths with George (played by Jim Sarbh), a bartender from Greater Kailash 1, an unexpected connection blossoms. As they share fragments of their pasts, their bond deepens, transcending fleeting moments into something profound and unspoken. But fate has other plans. George receives his long-awaited M.Tech acceptance letter, and in a moment of quiet heartbreak, Chitra chooses to step away, ensuring he pursues his dreams. Their farewell is sealed with a promise—to meet again at the same place, 20 years later.

Two decades pass. George returns to the same place, carrying the weight of the past and the anticipation of what lies ahead. But what he discovers changes everything. ‘The Promise’ is not just a story—it’s an emotional journey that lingers, reminding us that some bonds are meant to withstand the test of time.

‘The Promise’ stands as a testament to select filmmaking—where nuanced emotions, evolved storytelling techniques, and sophisticated narrative choices elevate cinema beyond mainstream conventions.
